<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="strxfrm" id="strxfrm">strxfrm</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
语法：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstring&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">size_t</span> <span class="kw3">strxfrm</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>str1, <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>str2, <span class="kw4">size_t</span> num <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

strxfrm()操作str2中前num个字符并将它们存储在str1中。结果是如果对str1和原来的str2进行strcoll()操作，你会得到和进行strcmp()操作相同的结果。
</p>

<p>
相关主题： <a href="strcmp" class="wikilink1" title="cn:string:c:strcmp">strcmp</a>, <a href="strcoll" class="wikilink1" title="cn:string:c:strcoll">strcoll</a>
</p>

</div>
